rows.label: bf02280100_0040
rows.name: Just need to apply energy charge to activate!

rows.label: bf02280100_0050
rows.name:
Tora, our friends' execution draws near.
There's no time to lose.

rows.label: bf02280100_0070
rows.name:
I know, I know! Okay artificial Blade,
it's wakey-wakey time!

rows.label: bf02280100_0100
rows.name: You can't keep calling her "artificial Blade"!

rows.label: bf02280100_0110
rows.name:
As her creator, the least you can
do is give her a proper name.

rows.label: bf02280100_0130
rows.name:
Actually, friends, Tora did think of name for her.
Very good name.

rows.label: bf02280100_0140
rows.name: Nice. Then I guess there's no problem.

rows.label: bf02280100_0150
rows.name: Well, why don't you introduce us, Tora!
